                    <li><strong>Diameter:</strong> 139,820 km (11.2 Ã— Earth)</li>
                    <li><strong>Mass:</strong> 1.898 Ã— 10Â²â· kg (318 Ã— Earth)</li>
                    <li><strong>Surface Temperature:</strong> -110Â°C (cloud tops)</li>
                    <li><strong>Orbital Period:</strong> 11.86 Earth years</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="info-card">
                <h3>Atmosphere & Weather</h3>
