                    <li><strong>Cloud Layers:</strong> Ammonia, water, ammonium hydrosulfide</li>
                    <li><strong>Great Red Spot:</strong> Giant storm (400+ years)</li>
                    <li><strong>Wind Speed:</strong> Up to 620 km/h</li>
                    <li><strong>Lightning:</strong> 1000Ã— more powerful than Earth</li>
                    <li><strong>Storms:</strong> Multiple storm systems</li>
